{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.1","label":"","reference":"Esdras 5:1","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.004.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.005.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">La construction du temple reprise<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-17: cf. (Ag 1; 2. Za 1 \u00e0 6.) (Ph 1:28. 1 Pi 3:12-15.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.5.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    Agg\u00e9e, le proph\u00e8te, et Zacharie, fils d\u2019Iddo, le proph\u00e8te, proph\u00e9tis\u00e8rent aux Juifs qui \u00e9taient en Juda et \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, au nom du Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5","name":"Esdras 5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.2","name":"Esdras 5:2","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.4.24","name":"Esdras 4:24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.4.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.2","label":"","reference":"Esdras 5:2","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.005.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.005.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.5.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Alors Zorobabel, fils de Schealthiel, et Josu\u00e9, fils de Jotsadak, se lev\u00e8rent et commenc\u00e8rent \u00e0 b\u00e2tir la maison de Dieu \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem. Et avec eux \u00e9taient les proph\u00e8tes de Dieu, qui les assistaient.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5","name":"Esdras 5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.3","name":"Esdras 5:3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.1","name":"Esdras 5:1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.3","label":"","reference":"Esdras 5:3","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.005.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.005.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.5.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Dans ce m\u00eame temps, Thathna\u00ef, gouverneur de ce c\u00f4t\u00e9 du fleuve, Schethar-Bozna\u00ef, et leurs coll\u00e8gues, vinrent aupr\u00e8s d\u2019eux et leur parl\u00e8rent ainsi: Qui vous a donn\u00e9 l\u2019autorisation de b\u00e2tir cette maison et de relever ces murs?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5","name":"Esdras 5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.4","name":"Esdras 5:4","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.2","name":"Esdras 5:2","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.4","label":"","reference":"Esdras 5:4","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.005.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.005.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.5.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Ils leur dirent encore: Quels sont les noms des hommes qui construisent cet \u00e9difice?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5","name":"Esdras 5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.5","name":"Esdras 5:5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.3","name":"Esdras 5:3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.5","label":"","reference":"Esdras 5:5","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.005.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.005.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.5.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Mais l\u2019\u0153il de Dieu veillait sur les anciens des Juifs. Et on laissa continuer les travaux pendant l\u2019envoi d\u2019un rapport \u00e0 Darius et jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la r\u00e9ception d\u2019une lettre sur cet objet.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5","name":"Esdras 5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.6","name":"Esdras 5:6","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.4","name":"Esdras 5:4","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.6","label":"","reference":"Esdras 5:6","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.005.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.005.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.5.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Copie de la lettre envoy\u00e9e au roi Darius par Thathna\u00ef, gouverneur de ce c\u00f4t\u00e9 du fleuve. Schethar-Bozna\u00ef, et leurs coll\u00e8gues d\u2019Apharsac, demeurant de ce c\u00f4t\u00e9 du fleuve.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5","name":"Esdras 5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.7","name":"Esdras 5:7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.5","name":"Esdras 5:5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.7","label":"","reference":"Esdras 5:7","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.005.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.005.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.5.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Ils lui adress\u00e8rent un rapport ainsi con\u00e7u:<\/p>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"it\">Au roi Darius, salut!<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5","name":"Esdras 5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.8","name":"Esdras 5:8","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.6","name":"Esdras 5:6","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.8","label":"","reference":"Esdras 5:8","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.005.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.005.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.5.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup><span class=\"it\">Que le roi sache que nous sommes all\u00e9s dans la province de Juda, \u00e0 la maison du grand Dieu. Elle se construit en pierres de taille, et le bois se pose dans les murs; le travail marche rapidement et r\u00e9ussit entre leurs mains.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5","name":"Esdras 5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.9","name":"Esdras 5:9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.7","name":"Esdras 5:7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.9","label":"","reference":"Esdras 5:9","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.005.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.005.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.5.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup><span class=\"it\">Nous avons interrog\u00e9 les anciens, et nous leur avons ainsi parl\u00e9: Qui vous a donn\u00e9 l\u2019autorisation de b\u00e2tir cette maison et de relever ces murs?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5","name":"Esdras 5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.10","name":"Esdras 5:10","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.8","name":"Esdras 5:8","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.10","label":"","reference":"Esdras 5:10","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.005.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.005.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.5.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup><span class=\"it\">Nous leur avons aussi demand\u00e9 leurs noms pour te les faire conna\u00eetre, et nous avons mis par \u00e9crit les noms des hommes qui sont \u00e0 leur t\u00eate.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5","name":"Esdras 5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.11","name":"Esdras 5:11","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.9","name":"Esdras 5:9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.11","label":"","reference":"Esdras 5:11","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.005.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.005.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.5.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup><span class=\"it\">Voici la r\u00e9ponse qu\u2019ils nous ont faite: Nous sommes les serviteurs du Dieu des cieux et de la terre, et nous reb\u00e2tissons la maison qui avait \u00e9t\u00e9 construite il y a bien des ann\u00e9es; un grand roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl l\u2019avait b\u00e2tie et achev\u00e9e.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5","name":"Esdras 5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.12","name":"Esdras 5:12","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.10","name":"Esdras 5:10","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.12","label":"","reference":"Esdras 5:12","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.005.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.005.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.5.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup><span class=\"it\">Mais<\/span><span class=\"it\">apr\u00e8s que nos p\u00e8res eurent irrit\u00e9 le Dieu des cieux, il les livra entre les mains de Nebucadnetsar, roi de Babylone, le Chald\u00e9en, qui d\u00e9truisit cette maison et emmena le peuple captif \u00e0 Babylone.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5","name":"Esdras 5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.13","name":"Esdras 5:13","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.11","name":"Esdras 5:11","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.13","label":"","reference":"Esdras 5:13","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.005.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.005.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.5.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup><span class=\"it\">Toutefois, la premi\u00e8re ann\u00e9e de Cyrus, roi de Babylone, le roi Cyrus donna l\u2019ordre de reb\u00e2tir cette maison de Dieu.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5","name":"Esdras 5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.14","name":"Esdras 5:14","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.12","name":"Esdras 5:12","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.14","label":"","reference":"Esdras 5:14","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.005.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.005.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.5.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup><span class=\"it\">Et m\u00eame le roi Cyrus \u00f4ta du temple de Babylone les ustensiles d\u2019or et d\u2019argent de la maison de Dieu, que Nebucadnetsar avait enlev\u00e9s du temple de J\u00e9rusalem et transport\u00e9s dans le temple de Babylone, il les fit<\/span><span class=\"it\">remettre au nomm\u00e9 Scheschbatsar, qu\u2019il \u00e9tablit gouverneur,<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5","name":"Esdras 5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.15","name":"Esdras 5:15","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.13","name":"Esdras 5:13","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.15","label":"","reference":"Esdras 5:15","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.005.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.005.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.5.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup><span class=\"it\">et il lui dit: Prends ces ustensiles, va les d\u00e9poser dans le temple de J\u00e9rusalem, et que la maison de Dieu soit reb\u00e2tie sur le lieu o\u00f9 elle \u00e9tait.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5","name":"Esdras 5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.16","name":"Esdras 5:16","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.14","name":"Esdras 5:14","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.16","label":"","reference":"Esdras 5:16","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.005.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.005.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.5.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup><span class=\"it\">Ce Scheschbatsar est donc venu, et il a pos\u00e9 les fondements de la maison de Dieu \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem; depuis lors jusqu\u2019\u00e0 pr\u00e9sent elle se construit, et elle n\u2019est pas achev\u00e9e.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5","name":"Esdras 5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.17","name":"Esdras 5:17","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.15","name":"Esdras 5:15","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.17","label":"","reference":"Esdras 5:17","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.005.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.006.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.5.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup><span class=\"it\">Maintenant, si le roi le trouve bon, que l\u2019on fasse des recherches dans la maison des tr\u00e9sors du roi \u00e0 Babylone, pour voir s\u2019il y a eu de la part du roi Cyrus un ordre donn\u00e9 pour la construction de cette maison de Dieu \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem. Puis, que le roi nous transmette sa volont\u00e9 sur cet objet.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5","name":"Esdras 5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.6.1","name":"Esdras 6:1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.6.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.5.16","name":"Esdras 5:16","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.5.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb580b900.19784717');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb580b900.19784717\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb580b900.19784717","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb580b900.19784717'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb580b900.19784717\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}